data.description: Beautiful remodel of this Split-Level Home! New roof. vinyl windows. some new exterior doors. LVP flooring, some new tile, new carpet, updated light fixtures, updated plumbing fixtures. Quartz counter tops throughout, all fresh paint inside & out! Entry way leads to main level and opens to large living with updated fireplace face w/gas logs, living also adjoins dining -both with view overlooking back yard and access to deck; and, on the other side, living opens to beautiful office area with built-ins. Kitchen has island with built-in cooktop, stainless appliances, pantry and nook that opens to dining for lots of entertaining room! Large master has walk-in closet & updated private bath w/tub and separate shower, secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets & updated Pullman bath. 2 large flex rooms in walk out basement with built-ins & large under-stair closet - Could be used as home gym, game room, theater room, additional bedroom, etc. Oversized 2-Car Garage with Extra Storage and Shelving. Lots of Space in the Backyard for Entertaining and Gardening includes a very nice shed with some new siding, new roof & fresh paint. 1 year Residential Service Agreement Offered by Seller.
